p: In the in vitro analysis against the SiHa cell line, fraction 14 presented an antiproliferative activity lower than that presented by paclitaxel. This suggests that the activity of fraction 14 may be related to the secondary metabolite apigenin, which was present at a higher concentration. Previous reports indicated that apigenin had favorable effects against carcinogenesis, metastasis, and angiogenesis by stimulating cell death by apoptosis or autophagy [ 30].
